@85   = ~(His features are dappled by the moon-shadows and the moonlight. They do not disappear entirely, but are almost unrecognizable in the night. His dark eyes are gleaming with silver reflections, like deep water. Just now you could read any expression on his face. Passionate, dreamy, stoic... nothing is as it appears under the moon. A small shiver shoots up your neck, a split second before Kivan's lips find yours. Some things do not lie, even under the moon...)~
