@243  = ~It cannot be all that bad, can it? I love you, <CHARNAME>.~
@244  = ~I know that you do, but it is *that* bad.~
@245  = ~It has nothing to do with love. But a hot bath can mend it, I think.~
@246  = ~Kivan, you are the only reason I can bear this at all. If not for you, I would have lost my mind already.~
