@302  = ~At least we elves do not grow beards.~
@303  = ~I had had bad headaches at the time when we first met, <CHARNAME>. The paste of henna herb helps with that when applied to the scalp, but it tints the hair.~
@304  = ~You, a'mael, are the best healing potion, though.~
